Author: notracisthasblackcat
Text: What about ones made with natural ingredients? For short term use?

Author: glugglugbiggulp
Text: I know I’m not Valid or anything, but I do work in healthcare and know that fucking with your fluids or electrolytes is a fast track ticket to the ER to receive said fluids or electrolytes via IV drip. Same with laxatives. I wouldn’t put this additional stress on your kidneys.
